NAME
    Monad::Maybe - A quasi-implementation of the Maybe monad in Perl

VERSION
    Version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
DESCRIPTION
    This is an experimental Perl implementation of a class with some
    properties of the Maybe monad.

  Methods
    nothing
    is_nothing
    just
    bind
    join

  Subroutines
    Nothing
    Just
    lift

AUTHOR
    Robert Rothenberg, "<rrwo at cpan.org>"

